hopobject.body: What line of work are you in? celoxmedical.com In 2007, a new Lindsay has emerged: Blonde, frighteningly skinny, and partying all over town with the likes of Nicole Richie and Paris Hilton. Lohan later admitted to Vanity Fair that her weight had gotten out of control at that time. 'I knew I had a problem and I couldn't admit it,' the singer-actress told the mag in early 2006. 'My arms were disgusting. I had no arms.' Lilo also said she was 'making myself sick' at the time - a claim she later said was 'misconstrued.'
